Jonathan Farwell https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jonathan_Farwell 0 Jonathan Farwell (born January 9, 1932) is an American film, television, and Broadway actor. He is best known for his soap opera role as George Rawlins on the CBS daytime drama The Young and the Restless.
